<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #F44336; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px; }
        .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; margin-top: 20px; border-radius: 5px; }
        .info { background: #FFCDD2; padding: 20px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 5px; text-align: center; }
        .details { background: white; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #F44336; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Invito Rifiutato</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Ciao {{ trainer.user.firstName }},</p>

            <div class="info">
                <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>{{ client.firstName }} {{ client.lastName }}</strong> ha rifiutato il tuo invito.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="details">
                <h3>ðŸ“‹ Dettagli</h3>
                <p><strong>Cliente:</strong> {{ client.firstName }} {{ client.lastName }}</p>
                <p><strong>Data Risposta:</strong> {{ invitation.respondedAt|date('d/m/Y H:i') }}</p>
                {% if invitation.rejectionReason %}
                <p><strong>Motivo:</strong> {{ invitation.rejectionReason }}</p>
                {% endif %}
            </div>

            <p>Non preoccuparti, puoi continuare a cercare nuovi clienti attraverso la piattaforma.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>FittyHub - Il tuo partner per il fitness</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
